author: Nick Vadala
title: Forbes Under 30 Summit kicks off with Under 30 Food Festival at Kimmel Center
text: Entertainment Forbes Under 30 Summit kicks off with Under 30 Food Festival at Kimmel Center New York's Joseph "JJ" Johnson took home the Best Young Chef title from Forbes' Under 30 Food Festival, which kicked off this week's Forbes Under 30 Summit Sunday night at the Kimmel Center with more than 750 attendees. Forbes Under 30 Summit kicks off with Under 30 Food Festival at Kimmel Center
